name: Paimon's Kamera
desc: A convenient gadget that can record and store pictures of scenery. This one belongs to Paimon. Aside from food and spending time with you, Paimon has many other hobbies, and photography is one of them. According to her, the pictures she has taken are enough for an exhibition. Perhaps one day, you can hold a photography exhibition for Paimon!

value.text: Used to take snapshots during the event "Mementos of Teyvat: Prelude of the Frozen Veil."
Version 5.8 Event - Mementos of Teyvat: Prelude of the Frozen Veil
